{
  "stem": "4693.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then, by night, they came and took us out of jail and put us on the train to Krasnoyarsk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With Russians, you never knew what happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I got to Krasnoyarsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, summer, I got on of one of the boats were going to Iran.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And again, the Polish gendarmerie took me from this and give me in the hands of the Russians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] From there, I came back to Bukhara.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I didn't want to-- shortly after I arrive in Bukhara, I had already papers because I had my release papers from the army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I could get a bread ration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Shortly after arrival, started the-- they wanted to force those who didn't leave with the army to take Russian citizenship on the basis that where they had the premises on the Ukraine and Belarus, 90-odd percent voted, Russians voting, for alliance with Russia.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I must have been one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously, this why I was-- I had to take Russian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they put me in jail because I didn't want to take it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was, for a few weeks, in jail.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I saw there is-- that I'm going to the concentration camp again, so I signed for the citizenship.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I sign for the citizenship, I got the work as a laborer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in a very short period, I was head of the Russian enterprise.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I started living very well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see, in Russia, everybody was stealing, from bottom to top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was stealing, too, but I have something to steal-- kerosene and soap, which is gold in the war times.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was doing very well, with the help of the police, and Communist Party, and everybody.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
